question: Lily is required to submit a 114-page dissertation. She already finished writing 1/6 of the dissertation. How many pages does she have left to write?
answer:
Lily has already written 1/6 of the dissertation which is 114 pages*1/6 = <<114*1/6=19>>19 pages.
So, she still needs to write 114 pages - 19 pages = <<114-19=95>>95 pages.
#### 95
